{"tid":227965,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"車路士4年前曾險簽「新亨利」","createTime":"2017-05-03T14:22:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T15:54:19.000Z","uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d1b5724a867ee798b69d71b25619a396465d6503","tid":227965,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T14:22:53.000Z","msg":"摩納哥前鋒基利安麥巴比現時在歐洲球壇炙手可熱，原來，英超勁旅車路士當年差一點就簽下這個「新亨利」。<br />\n外號「新亨利」的超新星基利安麥巴比（Kylian Mbapp&eacute;）年僅18歲，今季上陣38場射入24球，盛傳受到多家豪門，包括皇家馬德里覬覦。 據知，麥巴比4年前曾到史丹福橋試腳，車路士本可用17000鎊簽下，但最終決定提升青年軍蘇蘭基和阿巴謙上一隊，放棄購入「新亨利」，現在大概後悔莫及。 當時，麥巴比尚未加入摩納哥，仍在效力法國業餘球隊Bondy，其父是球隊主帥，誰也沒想過短短4年之後，其身價會飆升N倍。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf11c11ff663095ad72c74e82816874a8c59af4","tid":227965,"uid":2169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T14:23:31.000Z","msg":"好彩無簽<br />\n唔係又埋沒一個球星"},{"pid":"ecc55ac3a2ec06064cfccfc92b088c6543a440ce","tid":227965,"uid":17522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T14:32:01.000Z","msg":"其實車路士啲青訓好撚勁<br />\n不過冇機會上位"},{"pid":"ed81478c50f81f937f4b42c3e2c0ef91dafaabfa","tid":227965,"uid":70013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T14:39:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好彩無簽<br />\n唔係又埋沒一個球星</blockquote><br />\n無錯 簽咗應該係第2個蘇蘭基<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f8a66a51ee6d76090512735cf780673b257801a","tid":227965,"uid":993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T14:39:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實車路士啲青訓好撚勁<br />\n不過冇機會上位</blockquote><br />\n老鼠召喚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c4c60c9f044a272613820a906dd4d426f8d6ace","tid":227965,"uid":107611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T14:46:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實車路士啲青訓好撚勁<br /